1.00	Isabella_Toscano	Isabella Toscano	Isabella Beatrice Black (n√©e Toscano) was a fictional character on the NBC soap opera Days of our Lives. The character first appears on a recurring basis on October 16, 1989 being portrayed by actress, Staci Greason. Greason is put on contract in December 1989. Greason leaves the show in October 1992, after Isabella dies from pancreatic cancer. Greason reappears as Isabella's ghost in 1995, 2000, 2002-2003, and most recently in November 2010.	
